      <title>2024 年的股市波动率五年来从未如此低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/stock-volatility-in-2024-hasn-t-been-this-low-in-five-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[紧张的美国总统大选、中东和乌克兰的战争、欧洲政府的分崩离析：尽管出现了一系列风险事件，但股市波动率仍创下 2019 年以来的最低年平均水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/stock-volatility-in-2024-hasn-t-been-this-low-in-five-years</guid>
